statements: SELECT * FROM AlgorithmLogs;
SELECT algorithm_id, step_name, timestamp FROM AlgorithmLogs;
SELECT timestamp, log_message FROM AlgorithmLogs WHERE algorithm_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmLogs WHERE step_name LIKE 'init%';
SELECT algorithm_id, log_message FROM AlgorithmLogs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmLogs WHERE algorithm_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT algorithm_id, step_name FROM AlgorithmLogs WHERE step_name LIKE '%validation%'
SELECT * FROM AlgorithmLogs WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01' ORDER BY algorithm_id
SELECT algorithm_id, COUNT(*) AS total_logs FROM AlgorithmLogs GROUP BY algorithm_id HAVING total_logs > 10
SELECT DISTINCT step_name FROM AlgorithmLogs
SELECT * FROM algorithm_steps;
SELECT id, description FROM algorithm_steps WHERE step_number = 2;
SELECT MAX(step_number) AS max_step FROM algorithm_steps;
SELECT description, timestamp FROM algorithm_steps ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT step_number, description FROM algorithm_steps WHERE id = 3;
SELECT * FROM algorithm_steps WHERE step_number = 1;
SELECT description FROM algorithm_steps WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM algorithm_changes WHERE modified_by = 'John Doe' ORDER BY change_timestamp DESC;
SELECT step_id, step_number, description FROM algorithm_steps JOIN algorithm_changes ON algorithm_steps.id = algorithm_changes.step_id;
SELECT change_description, modified_by, change_timestamp FROM algorithm_changes WHERE modified_by LIKE '%Doe%' ORDER BY change_timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM algorithm_steps WHERE step_id = 1;
SELECT step_description FROM algorithm_steps WHERE step_id = 2;

SELECT change_description FROM algorithm_changes WHERE change_id = 3;

SELECT * FROM algorithm_changes WHERE change_id IN (1, 3, 5) AND change_description LIKE '%update%';
SELECT change_description FROM algorithm_changes WHERE change_id BETWEEN 2 AND 4 ORDER BY change_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM algorithm_logs WHERE log_id < 10 OR log_message IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM algorithm_logs;
SELECT log_id, algorithm_name FROM algorithm_logs WHERE log_id = 1;
SELECT algorithm_name, step_description FROM algorithm_logs WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM step_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT log_id, algorithm_name, timestamp FROM algorithm_logs WHERE algorithm_name LIKE '%search%';
SELECT * FROM algorithm_logs WHERE algorithm_name = 'Sorting Algorithm' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, step_description FROM algorithm_logs WHERE log_id >= 100 ORDER BY log_id ASC;
SELECT algorithm_name, step_description FROM step_logs WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, COUNT(*) FROM algorithm_logs GROUP BY algorithm_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT algorithm_name, step_name FROM step_logs JOIN algorithm_logs ON step_logs.algorithm_id = algorithm_logs.log_id ORDER BY algorithm_name, step_name ASC;
